*** init_hydro.f90 *** from mhd/init_hydro
### subroutine init_hydro ###
1. Discard any original passive scalars
2. if seed_high_T = true, turn on passive scalar for temperature higher then T_seed
3. if seed_pscal = true, call init_passive to turn on passive scalar at specific locations


# seed_pscal: insert seeds at specified locations at restart

# seed_high_T: insert seeds at region above given temperature at restart

# If seed_pscal or seed_high_T, allow for a different nvar at restart

