*** read_hydro_params.f90 *** from patch/collapse/read_hydro_params.f90
read passive scalar parameters from files

seed_pscal (logical): seed passive scalars at given positions upon initialization 
seed_high_T (logical): seed passive scalars if temperature surpasses some given threshold
i_seed (integer): number of seeds, must <= NPSCAL
T_seed (float): thresholds for high temperature recorder
evaporate_pscal:
T_evaporate:


from file "seed_passive.dat"
first line: nseeds
second line: seed_type * nseeds
0: point; 1: ring




